Mzansi content creators are about to be uplifted and see their content make good money for them. HOTT NOISE was launched on Thursday- the social media platform is said to be focused on uplifting Africa first.  at the launch of Hott Noise one of the Co-founders Nyiko Muchanga said: "Africa has a huge population and it's high time we take advantage of that."  "It is high time that that we celebrate our celebrities, and public figures." "This plartform is here to celebrate you, So we are all going to be happy, and we are all going to be celebrate," Muchanga said.